name: Digital Dream #4
description: The digital dream series is a play with textures, shapes and colors. This work was created combining computer generated imagery and photographs of various textures and objects from the physical world. The play of all the elements aims to create a balanced frenzy, that you can feast your eyes on and let your mind wander. This work is 72dpi, 9450 x 9450 pixels. Collectors in possession of this work can contact me for a full 300dpi image of the work, to be used at their discretion.
